These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, july
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis
There 2 different types of food: spinach, eggplant
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage       | mirinda       | cola |
| Birthday         | july | december  |
| Flower       | amaryllis    | zinnia    |
| Food   | eggplant       | spinach      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, motorbike
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, pakistani
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, kiwi
1. the russian is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
3. the russian is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | country     | indie |
| Transport           | roller | motorbike      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | russian      |
| Food         | lettuce | kiwi     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, mexican
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, blood-red
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann
House: wooden, gothic-revival
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the british is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Nationality      | british | mexican  |
| Color          | light-blue    | blood-red   |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | blend   |
| House     | gothic-revival     | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, magic-tricks
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Hobby      | singing       | magic-tricks |
| Pet          | goldfish         | hedgehog    |
| Game           | monopoly | bridge    |
| Flower   | zinnia           | iris   |

 #################################

 
