There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
