.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
House: palace, futuristic
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, japanese
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, pink
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
3. the indonesian is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | milk     |
| House   | palace          | futuristic |
| Nationality           | indonesian          | japanese    |
| Color     | pink            | emerald       |

 